title: Still no Pumpkin Icon? (Teemoing)
body: I know the icons for this event are still ongoing, but I haven't seen anyone get their pumpkin icon yet. Wondering if this one may have been forgotten.

replies.body:
I haven't seen them much either. o.O

However, we're still granting these Icons until **November 17th**, so if you don't have it by then, please [let us know](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
